{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Stagees is currently free and in Beta, and we are keen to get feedback and development ideas from users / testers !, for more details please check out the early access section.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Experience music in a fantastic new way ! Play any song in the world with 2-6 buttons. Choose an instrument and join your favorite band by yourself\u00a0or together with friends.\u00a0</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Use the buttons S, D, F, J, K, L in single-play to &quot;catch&quot; the notes as in a traditional rhythm game, but this time you are providing the sounds and playing side by side with your dearest artists. Correct player buttons for multi-play can be found under the FAQ section on the Stagees www homepage. For tutorials and other playing examples please watch the Stagees Youtube channel.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Although Stagees is a game-like music playing platform it includes some great educational elements. Go for it, challenge yourself and truly enjoy music like you never thought was possible.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Practice a bit and start to improve your personal best in single-play and be amazed how fun it is to play music  with friends using Co-op multi-play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Examples of users who will most likely find joy in using the platform:</strong>\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0\u00a0</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Persons who enjoy playing music games</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Persons who have a general interest in music or are involved in music somehow</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Persons who would like to learn and understand music further</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Person who might be restricted to play traditional instrument for instance due to an injury</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Persons who like to share or gather music experiences</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Persons who would like to play in a band</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Persons who know how to make music but do not play any traditional instruments</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Persons who would like to learn to make music</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Persons who would like to get inspired to try out other music instruments</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Persons who have ever dreamed of becoming something in music</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>No previous musical background required, go ahead and Just Play !</strong></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3473630/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738830452","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3473630/page.bg.jpg?t=1738830452","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3473630/563b0d58b73a9c60630aeb9b698b2988eb6a3d5f/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738830452","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3473630/563b0d58b73a9c60630aeb9b698b2988eb6a3d5f/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738830452","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen Co-op","id":39},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen","id":24}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Stagees is currently free and in Beta, and we are keen to get feedback and development ideas from users / testers !, for more details please check out the early access section.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Experience music in a fantastic new way ! Play any song in the world with 2-6 buttons. Choose an instrument and join your favorite band by yourself\u00a0or together with friends.\u00a0</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Use the b